    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty \u2013 it's basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken absolute pride in keeping it in pristine, flawless condition. No scratches, no dents, and that new-car feel is still totally there. It\u2019s honestly been my joy to drive, and I\u2019m only letting it go to a good home where it'll be just as pampered. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take a look!",
