    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine, collector-quality condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS to achieve a specific output of over 100hp per liter. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox to an M Variable Differential Lock. This vehicle has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance: the rear subframe has been structurally reinforced, rod bearings have been replaced with VAC coated units, and the Vanos system was overhauled with Beisan components. The chassis remains taut with refreshed bushings and factory-spec dampers, ensuring original turn-in characteristics. With zero fluid seepage and perfect compression across all cylinders, this is a mechanically superlative specimen for the purist collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
