    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving its stunning factory finish. The exterior paint is deep and lustrous, free of any swirl marks, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and carries that distinct new-car aroma, while every button and dial operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history detailing its pampered life. From the spotless engine bay to the untouched wheels, no detail has been overlooked. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a masterpiece in showroom condition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
