    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a museum-quality 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in Carbon Black. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six with individual throttle bodies, delivering a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides precise mechanical engagement, paired with a variable M differential lock for superior torque vectoring. This vehicle has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a subframe reinforcement and a full VANOS system overhaul to ensure timing integrity. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid, with factory-spec MacPherson struts and a multi-link rear setup that exhibits zero bushing deflection. With pristine paint depth and a concours-level undercarriage, this is an investment-grade specimen for the serious purist.",
